
### Get types names from schema

POST http://localhost:8080/api/graphql HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

query {
  __schema {
    types {
      name
      fields {
        name
        description
        type { 
          name
          kind
        }
        args { 
          name
          type { 
            name
            kind 
            ofType { 
              name
              kind
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

